  "description": "A nighttime view of San Francisco's waterfront featuring the Ferry Building and surrounding buildings. The Ferry Building, with its iconic clock tower, is prominently lit and displays the words 'SAN FRANCISCO' in large illuminated letters. Reflected lights shimmer across the dark water creating a vibrant, elongated display of color.  Modern skyscrapers rise behind the Ferry Building, illuminated with numerous windows that suggest activity within. The overall scene is a bustling urban landscape at night.",
